  <brief_title>A Modified Omental Patch Work Decreases Pancreatic Fistula After Lpd</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Modified Omental Patch Work Decreases Pancreatic Fistula After Laparoscopic Pancreaticoduodenectomy</official_title>
